                  , otherwise Allcock, not taken) for breaking the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17691206-16-victim202" type="victimName">
                           Stephen 
                           Kendrick 
                        <interp inst="t17691206-16-victim202" type="surname" value="Kendrick"></interp>
